      "title": "Alliance of Independents Support Dallas",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The alliance of independent parties represented by former ministers Wimal Weerawansa and Udaya Gammanpila has decided to support Mr. Dallas Agahapperuma in the election of the President to be held tomorrow (20) in Parliament.",
        "At the special press conference being held at the Communist Party headquarters in Borella with the participation of Mr. Vamil Weerawansa, the party representatives said that they support Mr. Dallas Agahapperuma."
      ],
